I feel kind of lost.

28:50.239 --> 28:50.860
I'm uncertain.

28:50.920 --> 28:52.281
I just, I'm lost.

28:54.504 --> 28:56.145
That can happen in your spiritual life as well.

28:56.986 --> 29:04.434
I think I got all things figured out about God and about life and about the future and I'm comfortable with who I am and what I believe in.

29:06.978 --> 29:11.082
And then maybe as you go along in life, you begin to have a little doubt.

29:11.663 --> 29:13.444
I'm not quite sure if I haven't figured out.

29:14.926 --> 29:18.069
And then one day, you know what?

29:20.151 --> 29:21.172
I don't have it figured out.

29:23.174 --> 29:23.694
I'm lost.

29:26.637 --> 29:32.242
See, lostness, people have recognition of lostness at different times.

29:32.823 --> 29:36.146
Some people recognize their spiritual lostness as kids.

29:37.154 --> 29:46.928
and others in the teenage years, and then others of us in adulthood, and sometimes way, way into adulthood.

29:49.631 --> 29:51.895
I've led people to Christ in their 80s.

29:53.617 --> 30:00.406
They're catching the last train, but they caught it because the shepherd loves them.

30:02.329 --> 30:04.312
Are you sense that that might be you today?

30:04.953 --> 30:05.874
That you might be

30:06.306 --> 30:06.947
a lost sheep.

30:06.987 --> 30:11.514
I mean, only you and talking to God would discern that.

30:13.196 --> 30:17.683
If you're a lost sheep and you realize today, I think I'm lost.

30:19.686 --> 30:22.791
The shepherd has gone on an all out search for you.

30:23.752 --> 30:28.419
And he has gone to the cross on your behalf, just like he searched for me.

30:29.301 --> 30:35.570
And I'm so glad that when I was lost, when I was at center, other people

30:35.778 --> 30:42.945
cared for me, introduced me to the gospel, and I met Jesus, and I trusted and followed Him.

30:43.005 --> 30:50.632
I'm so glad that even though I was a sinner, Jesus loved me, He gave His life for me, and I'm found today.

30:51.473 --> 30:52.374
I'm in God's family.

30:53.154 --> 30:55.577
And most of the people in this room would say the same thing.

30:55.657 --> 31:05.746
I'm so glad that even though I didn't know I was lost for a long time, that came a point where I realized I was lost, and I was found.

31:06.402 --> 31:10.047
I placed my faith in trust in Jesus for what he did for me on the cross.

31:11.009 --> 31:12.391
I believe that he died for my sin.

31:12.451 --> 31:13.793
He rose from the dead.

31:13.813 --> 31:14.654
He's alive today.

31:14.994 --> 31:17.778
And I said, Jesus, I trust in you.

31:17.878 --> 31:18.980
Please forgive my sins.

31:19.060 --> 31:20.903
And I want to be one of your followers.

31:23.767 --> 31:30.677
So I would invite you if that's if you're feeling like you're that lost sheep today, you could say today is the day.

31:31.198 --> 31:32.159
I realize, you know what?

31:32.259 --> 31:34.322
I'm lost, but I don't want to stay lost.

31:35.234 --> 31:39.019
because I know that Jesus loves me and I want to trust and follow Him.

31:39.499 --> 31:40.400
Would you just pray with me?

31:42.803 --> 31:53.216
If you sense that's you, if you sense that you really are that lost sheep and maybe you realize, gosh, you know, I've been lost for a long time, but I wasn't sure about it.

31:53.296 --> 32:04.530
I thought something different or felt like I had things figured out, but I realized that there's a lot more doubt about what I thought was right

32:05.922 --> 32:07.084
than there is truth to it.

32:08.165 --> 32:09.627
So I just want to trust Jesus.

32:11.090 --> 32:17.839
If that's you Lord, nobody can do that for you, but Jesus invites you to be rescued.

32:19.242 --> 32:25.010
Man, he went to a great extent to show his love for you, just like he did for me and everyone else in this room.

32:26.412 --> 32:33.202
If you want to be found, if you want to trust and follow Jesus, be forgiven for your sins, be adopted into God's family.

32:33.442 --> 32:37.287
and to have a permanent reservation in heaven for the rest of eternity.

32:38.449 --> 32:39.250
You can do that today.

32:39.791 --> 32:40.411
You can't earn it.

32:42.254 --> 32:47.801
You didn't deserve it anymore than I did, but Jesus offers that as a gift.

32:47.821 --> 32:54.310
If you'd like to receive that gift eternal life today, you can do so right now just you and God do it a little business.

32:55.231 --> 33:00.178
We just tell Jesus, if that's what you wanna do, tell Jesus, Jesus, I know I'm lost.

33:02.242 --> 33:06.247
And I thank you for helping me realize that.

33:06.267 --> 33:06.768
I'm a sinner.

33:09.131 --> 33:15.119
And I thank you, Lord, for loving me in spite of that and for paying the price for my sins.

33:18.343 --> 33:19.385
I believe in you, Jesus.

33:21.347 --> 33:26.214
Please forgive me for my sins right now and come into my life.

33:28.236 --> 33:29.618
Today,

33:30.786 --> 33:32.228
I want to become a fountain sheep.

33:35.973 --> 33:41.301
And I want to begin trusting and following you beginning today.

33:41.321 --> 33:43.804
Thank you, Jesus, for forgiving me.

33:44.305 --> 33:46.368
Thank you for bringing me into your family.

33:47.850 --> 33:49.292
Thank you for the gift of eternal life.

33:50.714 --> 33:51.755
In Jesus name, I pray.

33:53.258 --> 33:53.618
Amen.

